:SCALE
:VAR Regeneration Rate
:LINE-WIDTH 1

:GRAPH Population
:TITLE Population
:SCALE
:VAR Population
:LINE-WIDTH 3
:SCALE
:VAR Birth Rate
:LINE-WIDTH 2
:VAR Normal Death Rate
:LINE-STYLE DASH
:VAR Death Rate
:LINE-WIDTH 2
